<p>Drone and artillery strikes attributed to Sudan’s Rapid Support Forces (RSF) hit a school shelter in El Fasher on Friday night and Saturday morning, killing at least 53 people, with some reports putting the toll at 60 or more [aljazeera.com#1][straitstimes.com#1][japantoday.com#1]. A local doctors&#x27; group said the dead included 14 children and 15 women, and many victims had been sleeping in classrooms converted into temporary shelters when missiles struck [japantoday.com#1][nytimes.com#1]. El Fasher has been surrounded by the RSF for 17 months, and residents face hunger and starvation amid a siege that has tightened for over a year [bbc.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/sqT13OP8slB-5BmIWm3Z5NSyjaWHCkxW_sdcjl5tcwi-U3ZzeicfHiOQcbqmelqJ7HTuUUaVRvnnxnkviF2WCqwZnlZj1tEySoXy4jP5nB8OgedTNaxo_AoLmaprTM2oiR8U04-gXOPhm9wJQ7BrQHpVoK0UxP_VNLun-aTMPey4FOsq_Rpp7bDCyBtHv7KbY05p' alt='El Fasher has faced months of siege as civilians shelter in schools.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Casualty figures: A doctors&#x27; group reported at least 53 dead, including 14 children and 15 women, while activists and media put the toll at 60 or more [japantoday.com#1][aljazeera.com#1][straitstimes.com#1].</li><li>Weapons used: Reports describe RSF drone and artillery strikes on the area, with missiles hitting as people slept [straitstimes.com#1][aljazeera.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Targeted site: The attacks struck classrooms converted into temporary shelters at a school in El Fasher [nytimes.com#1][straitstimes.com#1].</li><li>Siege context: El Fasher has been surrounded by the RSF for 17 months, and the siege has tightened for over a year as residents face hunger and starvation [bbc.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Doctors&#x27; group in El Fasher: Reported at least 53 dead, including 14 children and 15 women, after the strike. (<a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/group-says-attack-by-sudanese-paramilitaries-in-darfur-kills-at-least-53'>Japan Today</a>)</li><li>Local activists: Said drone and artillery strikes by the RSF killed at least 60 people on Friday night and Saturday morning. (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/At-least-60-killed-in-attack-on-Sudans-al-Fashir-activists-say1'>The Straits Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/11/world/africa/sudan-shelter-strike-rsf.html'>Dozens Killed in Strikes at Shelter in Besieged Sudanese City</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/group-says-attack-by-sudanese-paramilitaries-in-darfur-kills-at-least-53'>Sudanese paramilitary drone attack kills at least 53 in Darfur, doctors&#x27; group says</a> - japantoday.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c3rvrn8req4o'>Drone strike in besieged Sudan city kills dozens</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/10/12/aftermath-of-rsf-drone-attack-which-killed-dozens-in-sudans-el-fasher'>Aftermath of RSF drone attack which killed dozens in Sudan’s el-Fasher</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/At-least-60-killed-in-attack-on-Sudans-al-Fashir-activists-say1'>At least 60 killed in attack on Sudan&#x27;s al-Fashir, activists say</a> - straitstimes.com</li></ul>